ooking a  touch harsh inorder to produce the thick shadows that give the game it's name, noting was visably irritating.Audio9/10The music and sound efects made for a very emersive experiance. The voice actors are the one thing that REALLY stood out. The suporting characters in particular very very expressive, especially for only being shadows on the wall. The main character's voice is a typical little girl's voice, and thus could be a bit grating, however she greatly reminded me of my little neice which made it almost endearing. Depending on your feelings about children this could be a scuff on your opinion of the game."
